Carrot and Orange Soup
  --Cristel

1.3 lb. carrots
1 potato
the juice of 1 orange
1.6 pints poultry stock
1 onion, thinly sliced
1 tsp olive oil
Salt and pepper

Peel and slice the carrots and potato. Heat the oil and onion in the saucepan over a medium heat for 2 min. Add the vegetables and cook for 5 more min, making sure to stir. Pour in the stock and cook for 25 min. Add the orange juice and blend. Season according to taste.


Notes: can add ginger



